description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Yulenka purrs with a rating of 84, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 168, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Box for East, Box for South, and 8 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80842-34484-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
